et","Date":"1978-90","Medium":"Gelatin silver print","CreditLine":"Gift of the Zofia Rydet Foundation, in memory of the artist’s brother, Tadeusz Rydet","URL":"https://www.moma.org/collection/works/492898","ImageURL":"https://www.moma.org/media/W1siZiIsIjYwMTQ5MCJdLFsicCIsImNvbnZlcnQiLCItcmVzaXplIDEwMjR4MTAyNFx1MDAzZSJdXQ.jpg?sha=096b3299258d5e43"}]